ou need.</div></div><div class="ebuOQ LG5iaf"><div class="dmlTCe LG5iaf" data-component-name='text'><div class=FSM3Ab data-component-name="rich_text">Every day is different. Get coaching that keeps you on track no matter what life brings, whether you’re managing sleep in a new time zone or adjusting workouts around an injury.<span jscontroller="wRcZid" jsaction="rcuQ6b:npT2md;pZY9Fb:cEy8ye" data-component-name="superscript" class="NhfhT" ssk='6:wZ7jae1#1'><a aria-label="footnote " aria-describedby="footnote:ghp" class="G4WAnd id-no-nav" aria-label="footnote " href="#footnote:ghp" jsaction="click:h5M12e"><sup></sup></a></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="TI4JMe DiZ56d RX40Xe" role="listitem" data-item><div class="lXKJdc"><div class="hFDEX" ssk='7:asset-0'><div jscontroller="B3Mtaf" jsaction="rcuQ6b:npT2md;" class="cRjosf" jsshadow><div jsslot class="nNTKid"><div jscontroller="YdWf3d" jsaction="rcuQ6b:WYd;" class=scQw1><div data-component-name="media_area" class="AIBajd DwbFB mmNbde RXBXye rqCAVb TT7lYc Ahc3gb" style="--gstore-component-media-area-aspect-ratio:6 / 7;--gstore-component-media-area-object-position:center"><picture class="GPlLTe" data-aspect-ratio="6 / 7"><source data-component-name="media_area_source" srcset="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/196uGXTC_h2qQIbLJQxFaFYtgrBZM8X6c7Q5bDjcjYpdBc5Gqv6BBJ86XREoCr-YDitY4Ss6SO86SCiHwBdW5CTcPb7WdveD0w=s3000-w3000-e365-rw-v0-nu, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/196uGXTC_h2qQIbLJQxFaFYtgrBZM8X6c7Q5bDjcjYpdBc5Gqv6BBJ86XREoCr-YDitY4Ss6SO86SCiHwBdW5CTcPb7WdveD0w=s6000-w6000-e365-rw-v0-nu 2x" media="(min-width: 1024px)"><img data-component-name="media_area_image" class="WeYPde" alt="A chat interface with Google Health Coach on a light blue abstract background. A user message asks, &quot;I heard heart rate variability is a good indication of health. How is mine?&quot; alongside a photo of a person checking his smartwatch. The Coach replies, &quot;With a steady HRV inc