built with Gemini."]],null,[null,null,[[null,[null,"ds-mid-emphasis-grey"],[null,"Explore Google Health Premium","Explore Google Health Premium"],[[null,"/product/google_health_premium"]]]]]]]],8],["XS - template_external_spacer [1776206877969-7]|IN(en-IN)|2026-04-14 17:55:29",null,null,null,null,"gsins_1307_5010",null,null,null,null,null,[[null,null,"extra-small"]],9],["Watches and Trackers - Gemini Coaching Feature|IN(en-IN)|2026-04-14 17:55:29",null,null,null,null,"gsins_8368_6781",null,null,null,null,null,[null,null,null,null,null,["w-and-t-gemini-coaching",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,["left"],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[null,null,null,null,[null,[null,"Built with Gemini to deliver fitness, sleep, and health coaching that fits your goals—and your life."],"display-small"]]]],10],["L - template_external_spacer [1776206877969-11]|IN(en-IN)|2026-04-14 17:55:29",null,null,null,null,"gsins_5185_1468",null,null,null,null,null,[[["background-gradient","background-gradient-FFFFFF","background-gradient-EFFFFE"],null,"extra-large"]],11],["Watches and Trackers - GHP features|IN(en-IN)|2026-04-16 00:06:26",null,null,null,null,"gsins_7686_9519",null,null,null,null,null,[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,["w-and-t-coaching-cases",[null,null,[null,null,"#EFFFFE"]],null,["fixed-height","mid","long"],[[null,null,[[["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6IqkcAxLb2CKgq9uTtfr3Aqd7t4xC1kGRLMQGVi9P8HeqpoWDJ2nxvLkiA2zi9D4qUFSNqpHGK9gIuJxTTQBm4w-zCUgpDomn8o",["lg-gt-only"],"A chat interface with Google Health Coach on a teal abstract background, accompanied by a photo of a person running outdoors. A user message reads, \"I'm travelling this week and will not have access to a gym.\" The Coach replies, \"Bring your running shoes! I'll switch your 2 indoor row workouts for outdoor runs.\"",[1200,1400],null,null,null,null,[0]]],[["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6jdLQqqR3BW1m05q0V_eekLkfJa7U9aYRlMorSE0fg3WwvmW9zRKR4rEA6o39Y9efiGiwhE6Liovo9vtMIimWr-HBfxJe4d-jpw",["md-lt-only","rounded-corners","disable-loop"],"A chat interface with Google Health Coach on a teal abstract background, accompanied by a photo of a person running outdoors. A user message reads, \"I'm travelling this week and will not have access to a gym.\" The Coach replies, \"Bring your running shoes! I'll switch your 2 indoor row workouts for outdoor runs.\"",[592,740],null,null,null,null,[0]]]],null,[null,null,null,null,[null,[null,"Guidance that’s always adapting to your progress."],"headline-medium"],[null,[null,"It all starts with a conversation. You tell Google Health Coach about your preferences and routines, and it follows your lead with longer-term fitness plans and day-by-day sleep goals.\u003csup data-footnote\u003d\"ghp\"\u003e\u003c/sup\u003e"]]]],[null,null,[[["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p1PkqA8-5umxKbvKHHnnMboeHJqdvtAIBzCVMAkr2j_lRL23G7NPmaScBXI5J900m5a_kUI6oqx6V1DtL_gQeDkstombuMaE5Vs",["lg-gt-only"],"A chat interface with Google Health Coach on a purple abstract background. It shows a photo of a person looking at their phone while sitting on a couch. A message from the Coach reads, \"You were awake just over 1hr 32 min, which is more than usual,\" followed by a visual graphic of a sleep tracking bar indicating \"Awake - 17%\".",[1200,1400],null,null,null,null,[0]]],[["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pCOuIIh8IkqUJJ6sOrJ8FxqSkFO9nA43Rn1U8AI_r5OZCF1XNkJWi09bwf6XAyBveJrK7-R6fTxbsZXvU1p4jvhq0H-F-T74RQ",["md-lt-only","rounded-corners","disable-loop"],"A chat interface with Google Health Coach on a purple abstract background. It shows a photo of a person looking at their phone while sitting on a couch. A message from the Coach reads, \"You were awake just over 1hr 32 min, which is more than usual,\" followed by a visual graphic of a sleep tracking bar indicating \"Awake - 17%\".",[592,740],null,null,null,null,[0]]]],null,[null,null,null,null,[null,[null,"Plans that adjust to the rest and recovery you need."],"headline-medium"],[null,[null,"Every day is different. Get coaching that keeps you on track no matter what life brings, whether you’re managing sleep in a new time zone or adjusting workouts around an injury.\u003csup data-footnote\u003d\"ghp\"\u003e\u003c/sup\u003e"]]]],[null,null,[[["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/196uGXTC_h2qQIbLJQxFaFYtgrBZM8X6c7Q5bDjcjYpdBc5Gqv6BBJ86XREoCr-YDitY4Ss6SO86SCiHwBdW5CTcPb7WdveD0w",["lg-gt-only"],"A chat interface with Google Health Coach on a light blue abstract background. A user message asks, \"I heard heart rate variability is a good indication of health. How is mine?\" alongside a photo of a person checking his smartwatch. The Coach replies, \"With a steady HRV increase over the last 3 months, your data is telling us what we want to hear.\" Below this is a chart showing a heart rate variability of 52 ms tracking \"In range\" across the days of the week.",[1200,1400],null,null,null,null,[0]]],[["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/HLVG8oKJM_OAbQUDHYoqcPJKnK_ayeCZr5ThzUNlOPRtkHtcPNGOuvvuXsfqvFmLFBYYXONzY7ds30ZVMj-qmuRooHypVdDhBw",["md-lt-only"],"A chat interface with Google Health Coach on a light blue abstract background. A user message asks, \"I heard heart rate variability is a good indication of health. How is mine?\" alongside a photo of a person checking his smartwatch. The Coach replies, \"With a steady HRV increase over the last 3 months, your data is telling us what we want to hear.\" Below this is a chart showing a heart rate variability of 52 ms tracking \"In range\" across the days of